.recharge-warpper
  .layout990.recharge.clearfix

    = render 'user_nav'

    .recharge-con.right
      %p.recharge-name 账户充值
      .recharge-list
        .recharge-progress
          .progress
            .progress-bar.progress-bar-success{"aria-valuemax" => "100", "aria-valuemin" => "0", "aria-valuenow" => "40", :role => "progressbar", :style => "width: 100%"}
              %span.sr-only 40% Complete (success)
          .progress-name.clearfix
            %span.active 1.验证身份
            %span.open.active 2.启用支付密码
            %span.right.active 3.完成
        .payment-password
          %p.text-center 支付密码已启用，使用账户中余额、玩艺币时，需要输入此支付密码
          .go-payment.text-center
            您现在可以：
            = link_to '充值余额', new_recharge_path, class: 'btn btn-primary'
            或
            = link_to '购买玩艺币', '#', class: 'green'